1183_128659_000017_000000 To "stump" another boy to do a thing is considered as putting a certain obligation on him to perform the action indicated.
1183_128659_000017_000001 The phrase is sometimes used, although the person giving the "stump" may not himself be able to accomplish the feat.
1183_128659_000019_000002 Once in Ohio several lads were collected together about a spring.
