201_122255_000037_000000 "Stop!" roared Little john.
201_122255_000037_000001 "Help!
201_122255_000044_000000 "And so thought I, also," cried Robin Hood, bursting out of the thicket and shouting with laughter till the tears ran down his cheeks.
