2384_152900_000010_000018 We attached great importance to having the bags made of the very best sort of skin, and took care that the thin skin of the belly was removed.
2384_152900_000011_000004 It is extraordinarily light and strong, and keeps the wind completely out.
2384_152900_000011_000008 The others consisted of trousers and jacket with hood.
2384_152900_000014_000000 Now, it is a fact that if one can wear soft foot gear exclusively the risk of frost bite is far less than if one is compelled to wear stiff boots; in soft foot gear, of course, the foot can move far more easily and keep warm.
