250_142286_000001_000000 MORNING CALLS
250_142286_000003_000000 mr Thornton had had some difficulty in working up his mother to the desired point of civility.
250_142286_000003_000001 She did not often make calls; and when she did, it was in heavy state that she went through her duties.
