250_142286_000003_000004 Yet Crampton was too far off for her to walk; and she had repeatedly questioned her son as to whether his wish that she should call on the Hales was strong enough to bear the expense of cab hire.
250_142286_000003_000005 She would have been thankful if it had not; for, as she said, 'she saw no use in making up friendships and intimacies with all the teachers and masters in Milton; why, he would be wanting her to call on Fanny's dancing master's wife, the next thing!'
250_142286_000005_000000 'Oh! you need not speak so hastily.
250_142286_000005_000001 I am going to morrow.
250_142286_000005_000002 I only wanted you exactly to understand about it.'
250_142286_000006_000000 'If you are going to morrow, I shall order horses.'
