250_142286_000010_000002 Now as for Fanny there, a little hardship would do her good.'
250_142286_000011_000000 'She is not made of the same stuff as you are, john.
250_142286_000011_000001 She could not bear it.' mrs Thornton was silent after this; for her last words bore relation to a subject which mortified her.
250_142286_000011_000002 She had an unconscious contempt for a weak character; and Fanny was weak in the very points in which her mother and brother were strong.
250_142286_000011_000004 A stranger, a careless observer might have considered that mrs Thornton's manner to her children betokened far more love to Fanny than to john.
250_142286_000011_000005 But such a one would have been deeply mistaken.
