2836_5354_000007_000006 She was looking like the ghost of her former self.
2836_5354_000007_000008 Her face was white and worn, her hands were thin, her eyes were sunken and surrounded by a black circle-care was digging caves for them.
2836_5354_000007_000009 A stranger might have attributed these signs to the state of her health; she knew better -knew that they were the effects of her wretched mind and heart.
