2836_5354_000056_000001 "I cannot help the delay."
2836_5354_000057_000000 "There has been no delay; quite the contrary.
2836_5354_000057_000001 But it may be expected hourly now."
2836_5354_000058_000001 I shall be back in time."
2836_5354_000059_000000 He quitted the room as he spoke, and Lady Isabel remained in it, the image of despair.
2836_5354_000059_000001 Nearly an hour elapsed when she remembered the breakfast things, and rang for them to be removed.
2836_5354_000061_000000 "Pierre was making himself ready to attend monsieur to England."
2836_5354_000062_000001 "Good bye, Isabel," said he, without further circumlocution or ceremony.
2836_5354_000064_000000 "Francis, have you any consideration left for me-any in the world?"
