2836_5355_000017_000002 It contained the information that the divorce was pronounced."
2836_5355_000018_000000 She spoke so quietly, so apparently without feeling or passion, that Sir Francis was agreeably astonished.
2836_5355_000018_000001 He should have less trouble in throwing off the mask.
2836_5355_000018_000002 But he was an ill tempered man; and to hear that the letter had been found to have the falseness of his fine protestations and promises laid bare, did not improve his temper now.
