2836_5355_000023_000000 He rose and began kicking at the logs; with the heel of his boot this time.
2836_5355_000024_000000 "Well, Isabel, you must be aware that it is an awful sacrifice for a man in my position to marry a divorced woman."
2836_5355_000025_000000 The hectic flushed into her thin cheeks, but her voice sounded calm as before.
