2952_410_000028_000000 In the same moment the head of the aruji, followed by the other four heads, sprang at Kwairyo.
2952_410_000028_000001 But the strong priest had already armed himself by plucking up a young tree; and with that tree he struck the heads as they came,--knocking them from him with tremendous blows.
2952_410_000028_000004 Kwairyo, however, as quickly gripped the head by its topknot, and repeatedly struck it.
2952_410_000028_000006 It was dead.
