3240_131231_000064_000001 Another peculiarity of this fall is that some of the fishes were much larger than others.
3240_131231_000064_000002 Or to those who hold out for segregation in a whirlwind, or that objects, say, twice as heavy as others would be separated from the lighter, we point out that some of these fishes were twice as heavy as others.
