3486_166446_000084_000000 The speeding shape halted, hesitated; it seemed about to return.
3486_166446_000084_000001 Crashed down upon us an abrupt crescendo of the distant drumming; peremptory, commanding.
3486_166446_000085_000000 Great gray eyes wide, filled with incredulous wonder, stunned disbelief, Norhala for an instant faltered.
