3699_47246_000003_000004 He might be slightly recalcitrant now and then, as is the habit of long eared pachyderms, under the thong of the fair Countess's tongue; but there seemed little probability that he would ever get his neck loose.
3699_47246_000003_000005 Still, a bachelor's heart is an outlying fortress that some fair enemy may any day take either by storm or stratagem; and there was always the possibility that mr Bridmain's first nuptials might occur before the Countess was quite sure of her second.
