3879_174923_000020_000010 "And so," said mrs Low, "you've begun to attack the Church?"
3879_174923_000020_000011 It must be remembered that at this moment mr Daubeny had not as yet electrified the minds of East Barsetshire, and that, therefore, mrs Low was not disturbed.
3879_174923_000021_000000 "You don't mean that I am guilty of throwing the first stone?" said Phineas.
3879_174923_000023_000000 "You haven't thrown the first stone," said mr Low; "but you have taken up the throwing at the first moment in which stones may be dangerous."
3879_174923_000024_000000 "No stones can be dangerous," said mrs Low.
3879_174923_000025_000000 "The idea of a State Church," said Phineas, "is opposed to my theory of political progress.
