3879_174923_000026_000002 It seemed, indeed, to Phineas that as mrs Low was buckled up in such triple armour that she feared nothing, she might have been less loud in expressing her abhorrence of the enemies of the Church.
3879_174923_000026_000003 If she feared nothing, why should she scream so loudly?
