3982_178459_000002_000000 As Bibbs came out of the New House, a Sunday trio was in course of passage upon the sidewalk: an ample young woman, placid of face; a black clad, thin young man, whose expression was one of habitual anxiety, habitual wariness and habitual eagerness.
