4018_103416_000002_000001 It was marked by an almost feverish gayety, as though, having apparently determined to pursue a policy dictated purely by self interest, the people wished to forget their anomalous position.
4018_103416_000002_000003 The vast number of war orders from abroad had brought prosperity into homes where it had long been absent.
4018_103416_000002_000004 Mills and factories took on new life. Labor was scarce and high.
4018_103416_000003_000000 It was a period of extravagance rather than pleasure.
4018_103416_000003_000001 People played that they might not think.
