4051_10927_000018_000000 Alexey Alexandrovitch paused, and rubbed his forehead and his eyes.
4051_10927_000018_000001 He saw that instead of doing as he had intended-that is to say, warning his wife against a mistake in the eyes of the world-he had unconsciously become agitated over what was the affair of her conscience, and was struggling against the barrier he fancied between them.
