4160_11550_000035_000000 She talked to her oftener, and seemed to listen while she talked, even though she was busy at the time.
4160_11550_000037_000000 When Theo went into the little back bedroom that evening to put on her hat, Priscilla Gower went with her, and, as she stood before the dressing table buttoning her sacque, she was somewhat puzzled by the expression on her companion's face.
