4160_11550_000041_000001 It was a feeling scarcely defined enough to allow her to decide whether it was real pain or only discomfort.
4160_11550_000042_000000 "I do not think I have any message to send," she replied.
4160_11550_000042_000001 "Thank you, Miss Priscilla."
