4160_11550_000048_000004 Business had called him away, and Lady Throckmorton, of course, knew what such business was, and how imperative its demands were.
4160_11550_000049_000000 "He might have waited," Theo said to herself, with an unexpected, inconsistent feeling of wretchedness.
