4160_14187_000049_000000 "But john Hornby may have had access to the previously made thumb mark of Reuben, and may possibly have obtained it; in which case he is almost certainly the thief.
4160_14187_000050_000000 "As to Walter Hornby, he may have had the means of obtaining Reuben's thumb mark; but there is no evidence that he had access either to the diamonds or to mr Hornby's memorandum block.
4160_14187_000052_000000 "Yes," replied Thorndyke.
