4267_287369_000033_000001 "I hope lightning doesn't strike around here."
4267_287369_000034_000000 The storm came on rapidly, but there was a curious quietness in the air that was more alarming than if a wind had blown.
4267_287369_000034_000001 The campfire burned steadily, and there was a certain oppressiveness in the atmosphere.
4267_287369_000035_000000 It was now quite dark, save when the fitful lightning flashes came, and they illuminated the scene brilliantly for a few seconds.
4267_287369_000035_000001 Then, by contrast, it was blacker than ever.
