4267_287369_000045_000001 "The lightning is attracted to it!"
4267_287369_000046_000000 His voice was swallowed up in the terrific crash that followed, and, as there came another flash of the celestial fire, the figure in white could be seen hurrying back up the mountain trail.
4267_287369_000046_000001 Evidently the electrical storm, with lightning bolts discharging so close, was too much for the "ghost."
4267_287369_000047_000000 In another instant it looked as if the whole place about where the diamond seekers stood, was a mass of fire.
