460_172359_000078_000000 I may say in parentheses that it was a favourite method in Mariposa if you wanted to get at the real worth of a man, to imagine him clean sold up, put up for auction, as it were.
460_172359_000078_000001 It was the only way to test him.
460_172359_000079_000000 "And now look at 'em," Jeff went on.
