460_172359_000079_000002 They give it away.
460_172359_000079_000003 And who do they give it to?
460_172359_000079_000004 Why, to those as don't want it, every time.
460_172359_000079_000006 Not a cent and never will."
460_172359_000080_000000 "I tell you, boys," continued Jeff (there were no boys present, but in Mariposa all really important speeches are addressed to an imaginary audience of boys)--"I tell you, if I was to make a million out of this Cubey, I'd give it straight to the poor, yes, sir-divide it up into a hundred lots of a thousand dollars each and give it to the people that hadn't nothing."
460_172359_000081_000000 So always after that I knew just what those bananas were being grown for.
460_172359_000082_000000 Indeed, after that, though Jefferson never spoke of his intentions directly, he said a number of things that seemed to bear on them.
460_172359_000083_000000 But still,--what's the use of talking of what Jeff meant to do?
460_172359_000083_000001 Nobody knows or cares about it now.
460_172359_000084_000000 The end of it was bound to come.
460_172359_000084_000001 Even in Mariposa some of the people must have thought so.
