4680_16026_000102_000000 She resumed:--
4680_16026_000103_000000 "I have only to cry out, and people will come, and then slap, bang! There are six of you; I represent the whole world."
4680_16026_000104_000000 Thenardier made a movement towards her.
4680_16026_000105_000000 "Don't approach!" she cried.
4680_16026_000106_000000 He halted, and said gently:--
4680_16026_000107_000000 "Well, no; I won't approach, but don't speak so loud.
4680_16026_000107_000001 So you intend to hinder us in our work, my daughter?
4680_16026_000107_000003 Have you no longer any kind feeling for your father?"
