4680_16026_000113_000000 She had set her elbow on her knee and her chin in her hand, and she swung her foot with an air of indifference.
4680_16026_000113_000002 The neighboring street lantern illuminated her profile and her attitude.
4680_16026_000113_000003 Nothing more resolute and more surprising could be seen.
4680_16026_000114_000000 The six rascals, speechless and gloomy at being held in check by a girl, retreated beneath the shadow cast by the lantern, and held counsel with furious and humiliated shrugs.
4680_16026_000115_000000 In the meantime she stared at them with a stern but peaceful air.
4680_16026_000116_000002 Is she in love with the dog?
4680_16026_000116_000003 It's a shame to miss this, anyway.
