4680_16026_000124_000001 All that's bad.
4680_16026_000124_000002 Let's quit."
4680_16026_000125_000000 They went away.
4680_16026_000126_000000 As they went, Montparnasse muttered:--
4680_16026_000129_000000 "I wouldn't.
4680_16026_000129_000001 I don't hit a lady."
4680_16026_000130_000000 At the corner of the street they halted and exchanged the following enigmatical dialogue in a low tone:--
4680_16026_000131_000000 "Where shall we go to sleep to night?"
4680_16026_000132_000000 "Under Pantin [Paris]."
4680_16026_000133_000000 "Have you the key to the gate, Thenardier?"
4680_16026_000135_000000 Eponine, who never took her eyes off of them, saw them retreat by the road by which they had come.
