5022_29405_000002_000000 THE RETURN OF THE PORTFOLIO
5022_29405_000004_000000 I betray no confidence in presenting this copy of his confession.
5022_29405_000004_000001 Time has passed since I first read it, and changes have occurred in the interval, which leave me free to exercise my own discretion, and to let the autobiography speak for itself.
5022_29405_000006_000000 Not one impression, but many impressions, troubled and confused my mind. Certain passages in the confession inclined me to believe that the writer was mad.
