5163_39921_000016_000001 And mrs Charley knows it too, although she can't prove it-more's the pity!
5163_39921_000016_000002 I don't say Isaac Cropper steals those plums with his own hands.
5163_39921_000016_000003 But he knows who does-and the plums go into Mehitable Cropper's preserving kettle; there's nothing surer."
5163_39921_000017_000000 "You see, Miss Maxwell, it's this way," explained mr Baxter, turning to esther.
