5163_39921_000023_000000 But a month later she had changed her opinion.
5163_39921_000023_000001 During that time the Cropper boys had come to school.
5163_39921_000024_000000 At first esther had been inclined to like them.
5163_39921_000024_000001 They were handsome lads, with the same smooth way that characterized their father, and seemed bright and intelligent.
5163_39921_000024_000002 For a few days all went well, and esther felt decidedly relieved.
5163_39921_000025_000000 But before long a subtle spirit of insubordination began to make itself felt in the school.
5163_39921_000025_000001 esther found herself powerless to cope with it.
5163_39921_000025_000002 The Croppers never openly defied her, but they did precisely as they pleased.
5163_39921_000025_000003 The other pupils thought themselves at liberty to follow this example, and in a month's time poor esther had completely lost control of her little kingdom.
5163_39921_000025_000004 Some complaints were heard among the ratepayers and even mr Baxter looked dubious.
5163_39921_000025_000005 She knew that unless she could regain her authority she would be requested to hand in her resignation, but she was baffled by the elusive system of defiance which the Cropper boys had organized.
5163_39921_000026_000000 One day she resolved to go to mr Cropper himself and appeal to his sense of justice, if he had any.
5163_39921_000026_000001 It had been an especially hard day in school.
5163_39921_000026_000002 When she had been absent at the noon hour all the desks in the schoolroom had been piled in a pyramid on the floor, books and slates interchanged, and various other pranks played.
5163_39921_000026_000003 When questioned every pupil denied having done or helped to do it.
5163_39921_000026_000004 Alfred and Bob Cropper looked her squarely in the eyes and declared their innocence in their usual gentlemanly fashion, yet esther felt sure that they were the guilty ones.
5163_39921_000026_000006 But she did not.
5163_39921_000026_000007 Instead she set her mouth firmly, helped the children restore the room to order, and after school went up to Isaac Cropper's house.
5163_39921_000027_000000 That gentleman himself came in from the harvest field looking as courtly as usual, even in his rough working clothes.
5163_39921_000027_000001 He shook hands heartily, told her he was glad to see her, and began talking about the weather.
