5808_54425_000008_000000 FRANKENSTEIN
5808_54425_000009_000000 Five years is but a short time in the life of a man, and yet many things may happen therein.
5808_54425_000009_000001 For instance, the whole way of a family's life may be changed.
5808_54425_000009_000002 Good natures may be made into bad ones and out of a soul of faith grow a spirit of unbelief.
5808_54425_000009_000003 The independence of respectability may harden into the insolence of defiance, and the sensitive cheek of modesty into the brazen face of shamelessness.
5808_54425_000009_000004 It may be true that the habits of years are hard to change, but this is not true of the first sixteen or seventeen years of a young person's life, else Kitty Hamilton and Joe could not so easily have become what they were.
5808_54425_000009_000005 It had taken barely five years to accomplish an entire metamorphosis of their characters.
5808_54425_000009_000006 In Joe's case even a shorter time was needed.
5808_54425_000009_000007 He was so ready to go down that it needed but a gentle push to start him, and once started, there was nothing within him to hold him back from the depths. For his will was as flabby as his conscience, and his pride, which stands to some men for conscience, had no definite aim or direction.
5808_54425_000010_000000 Hattie Sterling had given him both his greatest impulse for evil and for good.
5808_54425_000010_000001 She had at first given him his gentle push, but when she saw that his collapse would lose her a faithful and useful slave she had sought to check his course.
5808_54425_000010_000002 Her threat of the severance of their relations had held him up for a little time, and she began to believe that he was safe again.
5808_54425_000010_000003 He went back to the work he had neglected, drank moderately, and acted in most things as a sound, sensible being.
5808_54425_000010_000004 Then, all of a sudden, he went down again, and went down badly.
5808_54425_000010_000005 She kept her promise and threw him over.
5808_54425_000010_000006 Then he became a hanger on at the clubs, a genteel loafer.
5808_54425_000010_000008 He did not work, and yet he lived and ate and was proud of his degradation.
5808_54425_000010_000010 After some demur she received him upon his former footing.
5808_54425_000010_000011 It was only for a few months.
5808_54425_000010_000012 He fell again.
5808_54425_000010_000013 For almost four years this had happened intermittently.
