6064_300880_000014_000001 "It's a blockade."
6064_300880_000015_000000 "Hard and fast."
6064_300880_000016_000000 Among mr Harmon's many endearing virtues is this: he never asks questions about other people's troubles.
6064_300880_000016_000001 He now busied himself in thought.
6064_300880_000017_000000 "Haven't you any of your amateur theatrical duds here?" was the outcome of his cogitations.
