6385_34655_000018_000006 The rooms never came to an end.
6385_34655_000018_000007 All was deserted, silent, splendid, sinister.
6385_34655_000018_000008 It realized the fables of enchanted castles.
6385_34655_000018_000009 Hidden pipes of hot air maintained a summer temperature in the building.
6385_34655_000018_000010 It was as if some magician had caught up the month of June and imprisoned it in a labyrinth.
