6454_120342_000036_000001 O, we went to twenty places that night, I suppose!
6454_120342_000036_000002 We went to the grandest places in Boston, and we went to the meanest.
6454_120342_000036_000003 Everywhere they wished us a merry Christmas, and we them.
6454_120342_000036_000004 Everywhere a little crowd gathered round us, and then we dashed away far enough to gather quite another crowd; and then back, perhaps, not sorry to double on our steps if need were, and leaving every crowd with a happy thought of
