669_129061_000018_000004 To an affair of that nature, of course, he said, there was but one issue, and after his conference with his brother, he was going away to make the necessary arrangements for the meeting which must ensue.
669_129061_000019_000000 The elder brother was much affected, and shook Rawdon's hand with a cordiality seldom exhibited by him.
