696_93314_000005_000012 Will she marry someone else before I've earned the right to try to make her love me? afforded a see saw of reflection, agonising enough, for those small hours of wakefulness when we let our emotions play the primitive games with us.
696_93314_000005_000013 But always the morning brought strength to keep to his resolution.
