696_93314_000005_000015 And though he had denied himself the joy of speaking in words, he had let his eyes speak more than he knew.
696_93314_000005_000016 And now he had reached the wallflowers high up, and was plucking them and throwing them down so that they fell in a wavering bright shower round her feet.
696_93314_000005_000017 She did not pick them up.
696_93314_000005_000018 Her eyes were on him; and the empty place where her heart used to be seemed to swell till it almost choked her.
696_93314_000006_000000 He was coming down now.
696_93314_000006_000001 He was only about twenty five feet from the ground.
696_93314_000006_000002 There was no sound at all but the grating of his feet as he set them on the stones, and the movement, now and then, of a bird in the ivy.
696_93314_000006_000003 Then came a rustle, a gritty clatter, loud falling stones: his foot had slipped, and he had fallen.
696_93314_000006_000005 He was moving along now, slowly-hanging by his hands; now he grasped an ivy root-another-and pulled himself up till his knee was on the moulding of the arch.
696_93314_000006_000006 She would never have believed anyone who had told her that only two minutes had been lived between the moment of his stumble and the other moment when his foot touched the grass and he came towards her among the fallen wallflowers.
696_93314_000006_000007 She was a very nice girl and not at all forward, and I cannot understand or excuse her conduct.
696_93314_000007_000000 Even then he tried to be strong.
696_93314_000008_000000 "Don't!" he said tenderly, "don't worry.
696_93314_000008_000001 It's all right-I was a fool. Pull yourself together-there's someone coming."
696_93314_000009_000000 "I don't care," she said, for the touch of his cheek, pressed against her hair, told her all that she wanted to know.
696_93314_000009_000001 "Let them come, I don't care!
696_93314_000009_000002 Oh, how could you be so silly and horrid?
696_93314_000009_000003 Oh, thank God, thank God!
696_93314_000009_000004 Oh, how could you?"
696_93314_000010_000000 Of course, a really honourable young man would have got out of the situation somehow.
