7067_76047_000021_000000 There were some moments of silence.
7067_76047_000022_000000 "I am really very sorry to find myself in this dilemma," said Sir Richmond with a note of genuine regret in his voice.
7067_76047_000023_000000 "It is not a dilemma," said dr Martineau, with a corresponding loss of asperity.
7067_76047_000023_000001 "I grant you we discover we differ upon a question of taste and convenience.
7067_76047_000025_000000 "I could have wished," said the doctor, "that these ladies had happened a little later...."
7067_76047_000026_000000 The matter was settled.
7067_76047_000026_000001 Nothing more of a practical nature remained to be said.
7067_76047_000026_000002 But neither gentleman wished to break off with a harsh and bare decision.
