7067_76047_000037_000001 It is a sort of moral laziness masquerading as affection....
7067_76047_000037_000002 Still I suppose custom and tradition kept this girl in her place and she was petted, honoured, amused, talked about but not in a harmful way, and rather bored right up to the time when America came into the war.
