7067_76048_000044_000011 Don't you?"
7067_76048_000045_000000 "Now you tell me of it," she said with a smile, "I do."
7067_76048_000046_000000 "But before-?"
7067_76048_000047_000000 "no
7067_76048_000047_000001 You've made it clear.
7067_76048_000047_000002 It wasn't clear before."
7067_76048_000048_000000 "I've been talking of this sort of thing with my friend dr Martineau. And I've been thinking as well as talking.
7067_76048_000048_000001 That perhaps is why I'm so clear and positive."
7067_76048_000049_000000 "I don't complain that you are clear and positive.
7067_76048_000049_000002 It's refreshing to meet you."
7067_76048_000050_000000 "I found it refreshing to meet Martineau." A twinge of conscience about dr Martineau turned Sir Richmond into a new channel.
