7067_76048_000061_000000 She considered and turned on Sir Richmond gravely.
7067_76048_000062_000000 "Tell me what you want to do to him.
7067_76048_000062_000001 You find out so many things for me that I seem to have been thinking about in a sort of almost invisible half conscious way.
7067_76048_000062_000002 I've been suspecting for a long time that Civilization wasn't much good unless it got people like my father under some sort of control.
7067_76048_000062_000003 But controlling father-as distinguished from managing him!" She reviewed some private and amusing memories.
7067_76048_000062_000004 "He is a most intractable man."
7067_76048_000063_000000 Section three
7067_76048_000064_000001 She had had plentiful opportunities for observation in their homes and her own.
7067_76048_000064_000002 Gunter Lake, the big banker, she knew particularly well, because, it seemed, she had been engaged or was engaged to marry him.
7067_76048_000064_000003 "All these people," she said, "are pushing things about, affecting millions of lives, hurting and disordering hundreds of thousands of people.
7067_76048_000064_000004 They don't seem to know what they are doing.
