7078_271888_000058_000000 Spring came and went, but I saw very little of Dick.
7078_271888_000058_000002 Whenever he paid flying visits to London, however, he always looked me up, but, strangely enough, never mentioned Ethel. Nevertheless, I ascertained that they frequently met.
