7113_86041_000017_000000 'Sweetest and fairest of damsels,' cried the gnome, 'do not be angry; everything that is in my power I will do-but do not ask the impossible. So long as the sap was fresh in the roots the magic staff could keep them in the forms you desired, but as the sap dried up they withered away.
7113_86041_000017_000002 The great green patch in the garden will prove you with a more lively company.'
