7178_34645_000007_000012 Observe the design!
7178_34645_000007_000017 A man commits a bad action, and places his mark upon it.
7178_34645_000007_000018 To fill up the measure of crime by effrontery, to denounce himself, to cling to his misdeeds, is the insolent bravado of the criminal.
