7178_34645_000016_000000 In cases of doubtful descent, and of peerages in abeyance claimed by collaterals, the House of Lords must be consulted.
7178_34645_000016_000004 There was no point to submit to the House, and the Queen, assisted by the Lord Chancellor, had power to recognize and admit the new peer.
7178_34645_000017_000000 Barkilphedro managed everything.
7178_34645_000018_000000 The affair, thanks to him, was kept so close, the secret was so hermetically sealed, that neither Josiana nor Lord David caught sight of the fearful abyss which was being dug under them.
