7190_90542_000114_000006 I found such a man in Sir Henry Buckingham.
7190_90542_000114_000007 I told you I was not certain of my theory.
7190_90542_000114_000010 Yet his history coincided with my theory.
7190_90542_000115_000000 "Nothing."
7190_90542_000116_000001 "His mother was eccentric.
7190_90542_000117_000000 "How have you learnt all this?"
