7264_92316_000020_000000 Now from this fact arises a consideration of great importance to our subject.
7264_92316_000027_000002 True, the editor, being revocable and poor, could not pretend to full political power.
7264_92316_000028_000002 It had disappeared by the nineteen hundreds.
7264_92316_000029_000000 The editor became (and now is) a mere mouthpiece of the proprietor. Editors succeed each other rapidly.
7264_92316_000029_000003 It came quickly but thoroughly.
7264_92316_000029_000004 At last-like most rapid developments-it exceeded itself.
