7367_86737_000049_000001 "Excellency," cried the cicerone, seeing Franz approach the window, "shall I bring the carriage nearer to the palace?"
7367_86737_000050_000001 Franz was the "excellency," the vehicle was the "carriage," and the Hotel de Londres was the "palace." The genius for laudation characteristic of the race was in that phrase.
7367_86737_000051_000001 "Where do your excellencies wish to go?" asked he.
7367_86737_000052_000001 The day was passed at Saint Peter's alone.
