7367_86737_000055_000000 "It is much more convenient at Paris,--when anything cannot be done, you pay double, and it is done directly."
7367_86737_000056_000000 "That is what all the French say," returned Signor Pastrini, somewhat piqued; "for that reason, I do not understand why they travel."
