831_130746_000033_000001 THE MOONLIGHT RIDE
831_130746_000034_000000 And so the twenty minutes' law passed into an infinity.
831_130746_000034_000002 How they rode!
831_130746_000034_000003 How their hearts beat together and their breath came fast, and how every shadow was anticipation and every noise pursuit!
