8324_286681_000024_000001 They swim with their legs in the water, and with their wings in the air," said the biggest one.
8324_286681_000025_000000 "I don't believe it," said the saucy one.
8324_286681_000025_000001 "Anyhow, Eels run on land."
8324_286681_000026_000000 "Eels swim on land," said the biggest one.
8324_286681_000027_000000 "Eels run!"
8324_286681_000028_000000 "Eels swim!"
8324_286681_000031_000000 Then the two little Crayfishes, who had been talking louder and louder and becoming more and more angry, glared at each other, and jerked their feelers, and waved their pinching claws in a very, very ugly way.
