8324_286682_000025_000001 The Bachelor ate more than Big Brother, for his mouth was not sore.
8324_286682_000025_000002 But Big Brother was very happy.
8324_286682_000025_000004 It was the custom among his people to want to marry the best looking and strongest.
8324_286682_000025_000006 It is very hard for a young Mink to have the one he loves choose somebody else, just because the other fellow has the bushiest tail, or the longest fur, or the thickest pads on his feet.
