8465_246942_000004_000009 Their quietness is the relief brought by confession-even confession but to their fellows. Is it that the crime seems then lifted a little from their shoulders, and its weight shared by the ace?
8465_246942_000005_000001 But instead of such words of gentle might, like those of the man of whom he was so fond of talking, he had only spoken drearily of duty, hinting at a horror that would plunge the whole ancient family into a hell of dishonour and contempt!
