8465_246942_000006_000004 No; she would venture no farther. Sooner would she go to George Bascombe-from whom she not only could look for no spiritual comfort, but whose theories were so cruel against culprits of all sorts!
8465_246943_000002_000000 A HAUNTED SOUL.
8465_246943_000004_000000 She started when she saw him: some change had passed on him since the morning!
