8468_295198_000035_000001 You must alter your style a little,--adapt it to modern times.
8468_295198_000035_000002 Everybody now is a little touched with the operatic fever, and there's Tommy Oriole has been to New Orleans and brought back a touch of the artistic.
8468_295198_000036_000000 "Dear madam, consider my voice.
8468_295198_000036_000001 I never could hit the high notes."
8468_295198_000037_000000 "How do you know?
8468_295198_000037_000001 It's all practice; Tommy Oriole says so.
8468_295198_000037_000002 Just try the scales.
