8609_262281_000015_000001 Mind you fix upon me!
8609_262281_000015_000003 She is too young to go."
8609_262281_000016_000000 "It is expected to be a very interesting meeting," observed Constance, making no reply to Miss Caroline's special request.
8609_262281_000016_000001 "A gentleman who has lived for some years amongst the poor heathens is to give a history of his personal experiences.
8609_262281_000016_000002 Some of the anecdotes are beautiful."
