8609_262281_000026_000000 "I know," said Caroline, with some contrition.
8609_262281_000026_000001 "I intended to write it out this morning before you came; but somehow I lay in bed."
8609_262281_000027_000000 "If I were to come to you every morning at seven o'clock, would you undertake to get up and be ready for me?" asked Constance.
