8797_294123_000003_000000 War is to day the final arbiter in the affairs of men, and it is as yet the final test of the worth whileness of peoples.
8797_294123_000003_000001 Tested thus, the Korean fails.
8797_294123_000004_000001 The fields lay untouched.
