8797_294123_000011_000000 The Korean is the perfect type of inefficiency-of utter worthlessness. The Chinese is the perfect type of industry.
8797_294123_000011_000001 For sheer work no worker in the world can compare with him.
8797_294123_000011_000002 Work is the breath of his nostrils.
