8838_298546_000021_000011 The latest of these ambitious souls comes from the Wilson coal pits, which have undertaken to put up a stake of one hundred pounds and back their local champion.
8838_298546_000021_000012 There are various rumours afloat as to who their representative is to be, the name of Ted Barton being freely mentioned; but the betting, which is seven to one on the Master against any untried man, is a fair reflection of the feeling of the community.
